<i>♪ Get another piece of pie</i>
<i>for your wife ♪</i>

162
00:06:25,090 --> 00:06:28,257
<i>♪ Everybody wanna know</i>
<i>how it feel ♪</i>

163
00:06:28,293 --> 00:06:32,228
<i>♪ Everybody wanna see</i>
<i>what it's like ♪</i>

164
00:06:32,263 --> 00:06:35,098
<i>♪ I'll even eat a bean pie,</i>
<i>I don't mind ♪</i>

165
