<i>♪ Me and Missy is</i>
<i>so busy, busy making money ♪</i>

166
00:06:38,903 --> 00:06:40,436
<i>♪ All right ♪</i>

167
00:06:40,472 --> 00:06:40,942
<i>♪ All step back,</i>
<i>I'm 'bout to dance ♪</i>

168
